# Python Conventions

- Type hints on all function signatures
- No comments unless absolutely necessary
- Imports: stdlib → third-party → project modules (alphabetical within groups)
- Error handling at every system boundary (file I/O, USB, DBus, network)
- Use dacite for config dataclass deserialization
- Tests use pytest with timeout=60, thread-based
